Text: HYC stuffCarter Perrin is back from Italy will be sailing in the V races on Friday night He has promised Lira to any HYCers who can beat him on the racecourse There also will be a DJ Cash Bar Buffet afterwards so bring down your friends We are trying to beat the record of boats set earlier this summer We will be going to Taco Milagro Westheimer Kirby on Thursday night from PM We are attending the USA vs South Africa Rugby game at Robinson Stadium UH on Dec PM HYC Tailgate party BBQ before the game Purchase your tickets online at wwwusaeaglesorgticketsindexhtml DAMIEN GODDARD
